# Navigate Peptides — Compliance & Legal Requirements

> ⚠️ THIS IS THE MOST CRITICAL FILE IN THE PROJECT. The payment processor audits every page before approving the merchant account. The FDA has shut down vendors and prosecuted owners for language violations. Mastercard's MMP requires pre-transaction website scanning — no grace period. Every word on this site is a compliance surface.

## Three Overlapping Compliance Regimes

The site must simultaneously satisfy:
1. **Payment processor website requirements** (AllayPay / acquiring bank)
2. **Mastercard BRAM program** (card network enforcement)
3. **FDA "intended use" doctrine** (federal regulatory enforcement)

The processor requirements are the strictest and most immediately consequential — fail their audit and the merchant account doesn't activate.

